                "imgDesc": "<p>Artifact Definition: Consume <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">Sanctifying Elixir</span> to generate Artifacts of the designated <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">Set </span>and <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">Piece</span>, with the designated <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">Main Affix</span> and <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">some of the Minor Affixes</span>.<br>Artifact Extraction: Consume 5-star Artifacts of Lv. 4 and above to extract <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">Sanctifying Elixir</span>.<br>The amount of <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">Sanctifying Elixir</span> that can be extracted in a single period is limited, and each Artifact Set can be defined once this way per period.</p>",
